789785c43.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a99wrm85/pic_34/' target='_blank'><img alt="巧思玄关+mini衣帽间，精装大四居，空间订制也要精打细算" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202012/15/5fd813787a1ad5721.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">全部采用高腿设计，一体性强且方便<a class="seo_link" href="https://www.smzdm.com/fenlei/saodijiqiren/" target="_blank">扫地机器人</a>进出</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a99wrm85/pic_35/' target='_blank'><img alt="巧思玄关+mini衣帽间，精装大四居，空间订制也要精打细算" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/15/5fd813788ded68804.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a99wrm85/pic_36/' target='_blank'><img alt="巧思玄关+mini衣帽间，精装大四居，空间订制也要精打细算" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/15/5fd81378b4fce8348.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">业主自己搭配了类色系沙发和窗帘<br/></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a99wrm85/pic_37/' target='_blank'><img alt="巧思玄关+mini衣帽间，精装大四居，空间订制也要精打细算" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/15/5fd81378e28cb8590.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">玄关右侧是餐厅<br/></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a99wrm85/pic_38/' target='_blank'><img alt="巧思玄关+mini衣帽间，精装大四居，空间订制也要精打细算" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202012/15/5fd81378e280f5457.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">以大桌为中心，业主希望这里也能成为多功能区</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a99wrm85/pic_39/' target='_blank'><img alt="巧思玄关+mini衣帽间，精装大四居，空间订制也要精打细算" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/15/5fd81378e2d45469.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">日常聚餐，家庭会议，做手工搭乐高，可以自由切换定位</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a99wrm85/pic_40/' target='_blank'><img alt="巧思玄关+mini衣帽间，精装大四居，空间订制也要精打细算" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/15/5fd8137947dc59701.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smz